                <ab>
<lb n="1"/>śubham astu svasti śrīman mahā-rājādirāja-rāja paramēśvara rāyara kaṇṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> daka śrī rāya maṉō payaṅkara bhāṣaikku-t tappuva rāyara kaṇṭa
<lb n="2"/>śvara veṉṟa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> stāpaṉācāriya gaja vēṭṭai śrī-vīra-pratāpa śrī-vīra-catāśiva-tēva makā-rāyar prutivi-rājyam paṇṇi Aruḷā niṉṟa cakābtam 1481 ṉ mēl cellā niṉṟa cittārtti samvatsarattu tulā ṉāyaṟṟu Aparapakṣattu pañcami
<lb n="3"/>caṉi vāramum peṟṟa puṉar pūca nakṣatrattu nāḷ ceyaṅ koṇṭa cōḻa maṇṭalattu cantirakiri rājyattu <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> kōṭṭattu nakaraṅ kāñcipuram tiru vekā nayiṉār kōyil śrī paṇṭārattārōm śrī perum pūtūr Etirāciyaṟku cilācāsanam
<lb n="4"/>paṇṇik kuṭuttapaṭi ṉāṅkaḷ muṉṉāḻikku Uḻavaṭai kāṇippaṭi śāsanam paṇṇik kuṭutta Ik kārayaṉ tōppu meṭṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> maṉaip piṟakkaṭaikku teṟku rāmarācar tōṭṭattukku mēṟku ṉātar taricukku teṉ kiḻakku tama
<lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="8" unit="character"/> ṣa payat te <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> nilamāṉa Akkiṟāra<gap reason="lost" quantity="29" unit="character"/>
<lb n="6"/>tōppu tiru vekā nayiṉār <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> samaṟpikkaiyil Inta tōppu nilamāṉa <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> vaiccu teṉṉa maram māvaṭai maravaṭai payirātti maṇṭapamum taṭi Ira
<lb n="7"/>vāl vīccu vaṭakku tattaricaṉivākuṭi ṉūṟṟu muppatum maṭam nīkki ka …<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> koṇṭu namakku śiṣyar Āka naṭattak kaṭavō mākavum Emperumāṉ <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Eḻuntaruḷi maṇṭapattilē Amutu ceytaruḷa poliyūṭṭuk kaṭṭiṉatukku vi <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> tiru vekā nayiṉā
<lb n="8"/>tiru vāṉit tiru ṉāḷukku mūṉṟān tiru ṉāḷukku maṇṭapattilē Eḻuntaruḷi Amutu ceytaruḷa poliyūṭṭuk
<lb n="9"/>ṅa ney Uri cīrakam sarkkarai <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> yaṟṟan tirup paṇiyārattukku payaṟu<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/>vaṅa vellam
<lb n="10"/>Ōṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> tiruṉāḷukku perumāḷ Eḻuntaruḷi Amutu ceytaruḷum Appa paṭi ka kku
<lb n="11"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> U vaṅa tayir vaṅa kkum <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> Amutu sa <gap reason="lost" quantity="13" unit="character"/> Amutupaṭi
<lb n="12"/>…<gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> payaṟṟam tirup paṇiyārattukku payaṟu vellam līṭa pāṉakattukku vellam
<lb n="13"/>tta pu tirup pāṭi vēṭṭai kaṇṭaruḷa perumāḷ tirumpa Eḻuntaruḷkaiyil maṇṭapattil Amutu ceytaruḷa Appam <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> ku Amutupaṭi <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/>
